{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4d2e2f960f","title":"对乐天宇来信的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ecb07da1b8","index":0,"year":1975,"month":11,"day":24,"articleId":"4d2e2f960f"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji52","name":"毛泽东全集第52卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/52-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji52":{"comments":[{"id":"42d3010968","publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4d2e2f960f","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"乐天宇，农林科学家。早年在长沙读书时同毛泽东相识，1923年加入中国共产党。1975年11月18日，他给毛泽东等写信，反映原林业系统一些有派性的人要开除他的党籍的情况。信中说，“我全部历史，已于1972年经农林科学院派专员核实，并无任何历史问题”，请求中央“让我返回原借用单位（由中国科学院借调到林业部）工作，使我能于晚年尽绵薄于党的事业”。毛泽东的批语，就写在乐天宇的信上。"},{"id":"1b664050f8","publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4d2e2f960f","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"汪，指注东兴，当时任中共中央政治局委员、中央办公厅主任。1975年11月25日，他将毛泽东的批语和乐天宇的来信报送中共中央副主席邓小平等时写道：“建议请国务院政工小组调查报告。"}],"contents":[{"id":"4bc2533d86","type":"title","text":"对乐天宇来信的批语\"","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4d2e2f960f"},{"id":"42d3010968","type":"paragraph","text":"请注香一下此人情况","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4d2e2f960f"},{"id":"1b664050f8","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4d2e2f960f"},{"id":"1b17598e11","type":"paragraph","text":"十一月廿四日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4d2e2f960f"}],"page":{"id":"aac51da0bd","publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4d2e2f960f","start":105,"end":105}}}},"__N_SSG":true}